name: book_model
sql:
CREATE TABLE `book_model` (
  `cover` TEXT,
  `path` TEXT,
  `chapter` TEXT,
  `wordCount` INTEGER,
  `md5_id` TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
  `author` TEXT,
  `description` TEXT,
  `title` TEXT,
  `last_index` INTEGER,
  `last_offset` DOUBLE,
  `chapter_count` INTEGER
, test_key2 String)
